5
00:00:16,260 --> 00:00:20,260
and key takeaway messages of this week.

6
00:00:20,260 --> 00:00:22,690
so this week, we looked at sanitation.

7
00:00:22,690 --> 00:00:25,030
we learned the definition of sanitation;

8
00:00:25,030 --> 00:00:27,436
what a sanitation system is;

9
00:00:27,436 --> 00:00:29,313
and its different elements.

10
00:00:29,313 --> 00:00:34,010
We explored sanitation product terminology
and functional groups

11
00:00:34,010 --> 00:00:37,510
then we moved to excrete the management
in humanitarian crisis

12
00:00:37,510 --> 00:00:41,260
where we presented an example
