13
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:45,500
can be developed over the course of
humanitarian response;

14
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:49,970
starting from the acute phase of response
that is fair minimal standards apply

15
00:00:49,970 --> 00:00:54,770
to rehabilitation of existing infrastructure
in the recovery period.

16
00:00:54,770 --> 00:00:58,770
Finally, we looked at which selection
criteria need to be considered

17
00:00:58,770 --> 00:01:01,950
